rägnante Aspekte kennzeichnen das Sammelwerk insgesamt: die exemplarische Hinwendung zur norditalienischen Kultur als solcher; ein perspektivisches Spektrum, das sich unterschiedlichen Disziplinen verdankt und über den Kreis der Beiträger verschiedenartige Forschungstraditionen vereint; die prozessual bestimmte Rahmenperspektive (Rezeption, Adaptation, Transformation) in ihrer die Erkenntnis leitenden Dynamik.  aThis collective volume deals with the reception and assimilation of different forms of knowledge in Northern Italy in the 18th and early 19th centuries. This knowledge originated in Germany, Austria and France and was communicated through literature. The aim of this book is to show the European significance of Northern Italy as hub of cultural mediation and assimilation processes - a role which has received little attention until now.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Italian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aAufklärung. 4aNorditalien. 4aRomantik. 4aWissenstransfer. 4akulturelle Identität. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aCultural Identity.  aEnlightenment.  aKnowledge Transfer.  aNorthern Italy.  aRomanticism.1 aBrugnolo, Furio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrugnolo, Furio, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBruni, Arnaldo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaliaro, Ilvano, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCamerino, Giuseppe A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aColombo, Angelo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aContarini, Silvia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCremante, Renzo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFabris, Angela,